{"word":"κνεφαῖος","slug":"κνεφαῖος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κνεφαῖος</b></el> <el>(κνεφαῖος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κνέφας'><el>κνέφας</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>dark, dusky</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>in the dark, early in the morning</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}